{"tid":1002691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台驗出大陸口罩致癌　無法防霾","createTime":"2019-01-31T06:37:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T06:45:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"69bd6df13f9d62323c6ab53be394cea89c9c614b","tid":1002691,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:37:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190131/20602903\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190131%2F20602903&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6hPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=9b8023bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190131%2F20602903&h=ff2934e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190131/20602903</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月31日 <br />\n<br />\n台驗出大陸口罩致癌　無法防霾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190131/large/a1503a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190131%2Flarge%2Fa1503a.gif&h=52308dfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩款大陸製口罩驗出致癌物超標。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣近月空氣污染嚴重，市民外出時戴口罩自保。台灣行政院消費者保護處（消保處）昨日最新公佈口罩品質檢測結果，在25件樣本中，只有2件品質及標示完全符合規定，其餘23件樣本品質不合格，包括無法證明有防霾效果，不合格率超過9成，其中2款大陸製口罩致癌物偶氮色料超標，戴了不僅無法防霾，還可能致癌。<br />\n<br />\n台灣消保處對市面25款聲稱防霾（PM2.5）口罩，包括4款醫用口罩及21款一般口罩，進行品質測試，發現有17件品質檢測不合格，包括不符當地CNS15980標準「粒狀物防護效果」、「過濾效率」及「呼吸阻抗」。22件標示不合規定，只有兩件品質與標示都合格，分別是「萊潔PM2.5防霾口罩」及「格安德摺叠式口罩」，同屬台灣製，售價分別99新台幣（約25港元）及23元（約6港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190131/large/a1503b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190131%2Flarge%2Fa1503b.gif&h=dcbf8a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣空氣欠佳，佩戴口罩成市民外出指定動作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n致癌物超標逾兩倍<br />\n<br />\n消保處抽驗發現，「AsaBuru」PM2.5防塵保暖過濾口罩及coni mall的QDY七朵雲「防霧霾立體剪裁口罩PM2.5」樣本，驗出致癌物偶氮色料超標。偶氮色料已確認有致癌性，用在布料上不得超過20mg（毫克）/kg，但2款口罩都超標兩倍以上。台北榮總臨床毒物與職業醫學科主任楊振昌表示，偶氮色料為工業用着色劑，為人體第一級致癌物，長期接觸會增加膀胱癌風險，也容易引起皮膚、鼻子過敏。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n「作大市長」倡建迪士尼開發石油"},{"pid":"8b2a7ee5e77c0a2cc9cce5562ed600ebd433b8fd","tid":1002691,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:39:23.000Z","msg":"另一種方式殺死人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc0e93d5f0088b480b0f627920515b8c8ee22cf","tid":1002691,"uid":195995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:40:50.000Z","msg":"以毒攻毒你識條鐵咩"},{"pid":"5a9762f1f3475e6f18eea74453587eb09e80e5fd","tid":1002691,"uid":151531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:41:01.000Z","msg":"戴又死 唔戴都死"},{"pid":"cd0331784604c4583c7290e9d84031118b983044","tid":1002691,"uid":55758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a9762f1f3475e6f18eea74453587eb09e80e5fd","tid":1002691,"uid":151531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:41:01.000Z","msg":"戴又死 唔戴都死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:43:00.000Z","msg":"帶一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf17bb915b26ee3cf48bdf97b2679a46fd0d3ec","tid":1002691,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:45:45.000Z","msg":"「作大市長」倡建迪士尼開發石油<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順手貼埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}